instruction: Create a data model to store information about different books.
output:
The data model could include the following fields, each of them representing a different category of data to be stored:

- Book title 
- Book author 
- Publication date 
- Number of pages 
- Genre 
- Recommended age range 
- ISBN 
- Publisher 
- Series 
- Illustrated 
- Language 
- Binding 
- Edition 
- Audience 
- Availability of ebook version 
- Price 
- Year of release 
- Rating 
- Book cover 
- Reviews 
- Number of copies sold 
- Author bio
